	so add them now.

2011-11-28   Dan McMahill * dan AT mcmahill dot net *

	* configure.ac: Check for dlopen in -ldl.  This is used by the
	TinyScheme dynamic loader (src/dynload.c).  Fixes linking problems
	seen on some systems like Fedora 16.

