2009-02-16   Dan McMahill * dan AT mcmahill dot net *

	* src/callbacks.c, src/drill.c, src/drill_stats.c, src/gerbv.h: Add
	a total drill count for the whole board to the drill stats.  Keep
	stats on 'R' codes (repeat) in the drill files.  For now (until I
	complete implementing R support), give a warning that the R command
	is ignored.

