	sequentially, ignoring any skipped layer numbers. This should help
	make gerbv more robust against faulty project files.

2008-08-28   Stuart Brorson * sdb AT cloud9 dot net *

	* src/callbacks.c: Move "are you sure" dialog to before file chooser
	dialog is run in open_project.  This is the more logical order:
	Warn the user first, and then let him chose the file.  The other
	order didn't work in the case where the user hit "cancel" in the
	file chooser, because it would ask "are you sure" after the user hit
	cancel.

