2008-08-26   Stuart Brorson * sdb AT cloud9 dot net *

	* AUTHORS, BUGS, NEWS, README, README-release.txt, src/Makefile.am,
	src/callbacks.c, src/callbacks.h, src/interface.c: Made BUGS file
