2008-08-24   Stuart Brorson * sdb AT cloud9 dot net *

	* src/callbacks.c, src/gerbv.c, src/interface.c: Moved project
	related stuff in "file" menu to top section, and layer stuff to
	second section.  This is because "new" is traditionally the top menu
	item, and it creates a new project.   Therefore, all project stuff
	must be at top.  Also did minor refactoring of revert function calls
	to eliminate a compiler warning.

