2008-08-21   Julian Lamb * thepurlieu AT gmail dot com *

	* src/main.c: * change default render mode to cairo on Windows builds, since all
	data points seem to show it renders faster than GDK. This should
	help speed up the speed for the casual user that doesn't change the
	render mode.

