	needed by libgerbv previously).  * Change mainProject to use a pointer, and move all gerbv_project_t
	initialization to a function called gerbv_create_project. This
	affected almost all the GUI source code files.  * Add a first example file to show how to use libgerbv in other
	software (doc/example-code/exampl1.c).  * Start filling in the documentation inside gerbv.h.  To create the
	documentation, run "doxygen doc/Doxyfile.nopreprocessing" from the
	root directory, and then view the documentation at
	doc/html/index.html.

