	line, effectively allowing panelization of multiple files (or
	multiple instances of the same file). e.g.: src/gerbv --export=rs274x --output=output.gbx --translate=0,0
	--translate=3.5,0 example/dan/top.gbx example/dan/top.gbx to panelize 2 copies of top.gpx next to each other.

