2008-01-22   Julian Lamb * thepurlieu AT gmail dot com *

	* src/export-rs274x.c: round values before writing to file in order
	to make sure no truncation errors are included.

2008-01-22   Julian Lamb * thepurlieu AT gmail dot com *

	* src/Makefile.am, src/export-rs274x.c, src/export-rs274x.h,
	src/gerbv.c: *export-rs274x.[ch]: start coding the library to export
		a gerb_image to a Gerber file. Currently it supports basic aperture
		drawing and polygon fills without circular paths inside them. This
		should support most all files exported from PCB, though. For now,
		only the command line option is hooked into this new library for
	testing (--export-rs274x).

