2007-12-14   Stuart Brorson * sdb AT cloud9 dot net *

	* ChangeLog, src/callbacks.c, src/callbacks.h, src/draw-gdk.c,
	src/draw-gdk.h, src/drill.c, src/gerb_image.c, src/gerb_image.h,
