		  when project file has layer files that won't load.  	* src/callbacks.[ch],src/interface.c,src/render.[ch]: Big 	  cleanup of callbacks.c and start moving zoom code to render.c in 	  preparation for separating out zoom info from screen struct
		  (allowing for exporting to file and improving code readability).
