2007-11-26   Stuart Brorson * sdb AT cloud9 dot net *

	* configure.in, src/drill.c: Modify dprintf to make it configurable
	from config.h.  This makes it possible to turn on and off for all
	files using this fcn.

2007-11-26   Dan McMahill * dan AT mcmahill dot net *

	* configure.in: Instead of completely overriding CFLAGS and LIBS,
	just append our stuff.  Now we don't lose our compiler optimizations
	and any user supplied flags.  Also add a --enable-debug argument which defines DEBUG=1 in
	config.h.

2007-11-26   Stuart Brorson * sdb AT cloud9 dot net *

	* src/gerbv.c, src/gerbv_screen.h: Added help->about dialog.

