2007-11-19   Julian Lamb * thepurlieu AT gmail dot com *

	* ChangeLog, configure.in, example/am-test/am-test.gbx, src/draw.c,
	src/draw.h, src/gerbv.c, src/pick-and-place.c: 	* complete the rendering conversion to cairo. Everything that
		  rendered before *should* still render correctly. If it doesn't let
		  me know. As a side note, several rendering bugs were discovered in
		  the aperature macro code, so those are now fixed.  	* add an extra sanity check in the pick-n-place file parser and
		  help make sure it doesn't incorrectly guess the filetype 	* add a cairo check to configure.in

