	example/protel-pnp/SE_SG_IF_V2.apr,
	example/protel-pnp/Status_Report.txt: These examples of GERBER files
	with matching "pick and place".csv file are intented to demonstrate
	possible usage of gerbv in PCB assembly and any other work which
	requires efficient searching of elements on PCB.   They were donated by Karl Schmittschneider * ks dot electronic AT
	t-online dot de * to gerbv project on 2005-04-19.

