2002-05-02   Anders Eriksson * aenfaldor AT users dot sourceforge dot net *

	* src/gerbv.c: Make sure the event is sent to the zoom function when
	zooming around mouse.  Attempt to be preemptive when converting
	image to pixmap. This gives a small gain in responsiveness, but it
	is all we have time to do this close to the next release. Note that
	constantly moving the mouse will prevent screen updates to happen.
	Can we live with this? To be improved.

